videos.description: Alex Robinson impresses with a nice behind-the-back dish to Kevin Samuel who rises up and posterizes his Longhorn defender for an early TCU slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Robinson's sweet dish sets up Samuel's poster slam) 2019/4/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson's sweet dish sets up Samuel's poster slam

videos.description: Dylan Osetkowski spots up for a 3-pointer from the top of the arc to put Texas back up 14 over TCU in the NIT Semifinals.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Osetkowski drains the dagger 3 for Texas) 2019/4/2 ESHEET
